The Oval Pinky Signet — a modern heirloom designed for daily wear, a consideration of wearable symbols of identity. Wear it blank or personalized with an engraving of your choice.

#jhannah #jhannahjewelry #pinkysignet #signetring

Introducing a nail polish collaboration between @j.hannah & @lacma, with two new shades specifically sampled from the 1671 still life Flowers in a Glass Vase by Dirck de Bray. The painting, considered one of de Bray’s masterpieces, is part of the 2023-24 exhibition “The World Made Wondrous.”

The exclusive shades include: Morning Glory (a painterly azure) & Hollyhock (a blushy, sun-ripe apricot), with both available now in limited edition at LACMA and on jhannahjewelry.com.

#lacma #lacmastore #jhannahnailpolish

NEW: In collaboration with A24, we are so excited to introduce The Priscilla Locket, a classic heart-shaped locket strung on a silk ribbon, created for Sofia Coppola’s 2023 film “Priscilla.” 

Inspired by the heart-shaped version featured in the film by costume designer Stacey Battat, our reinterpretation is intended as an elegant & personalized keepsake, opening to display a meaningful miniature photo or petite talisman of your choosing. The Priscilla Locket arrives detailed with a subtle, commemorative Priscilla script engraving on the back.

Now available exclusively on jhannahjewelry.com in 14k white or yellow gold & in sterling silver available via @a24 

#jhannah #a24 #priscillamovie #sofiacoppola #heartlocket

Studio selections — A pair of our Intaglio Class Rings in 14k yellow recycled gold & hand carved quartz, customized with a special sentiment for our clients.

A reimagining of tradition-steeped collegiate rings, as interpreted through the JH lens: preserving their personalized charm and pleasing substantiality while elevating through with subtle detail, pared-back form, and refined materials. We love how it looks worn as a timelessly chic (and subtly statement-making) pinky ring, or even strung onto a chain and worn as a pendant.

Intended to be personalized through specificity, every ring is designed to come to life through a layered pairing of words, initials, and/or symbols of your choosing. 

#jhannah #classring #customjewelry

Ornamentation for living, crafted through a jewelry designer’s lens.

The J.Hannah Table Lamp 01 & 02, part of our inaugural lighting collection—an extension of the ethos and inspirations behind our fine jewelry, exploring the elegantly substantial; pared back modernism; and architectural geometry.

#jhannah #lightingdesign #interiordesign #homedecor

The Baby Pearl Strands — Delicate strands of hand-strung (locally!), freshwater pearls, secured with a solid 14k gold clasp. Available in a suite of lengths, to be worn on the neck, wrist, or ankle. A handful available in stock and ready to ship!

#jhannah #jhannahjewelry #seedpearls #pearljewelry

NEW! The latest addition to the JH classics: The Baby Pearl Strands.
 
Delicate strands of hand-strung, freshwater pearls, secured with a solid 14k gold clasp. The Baby Pearl Strands are available in a suite of lengths for the neck, wrist, or ankle.
 
Wear as a casual, refined layer, or with a personalized pendant for a lustrous alternative to a classic chain.

As with most of our fine jewelry, the Baby Pearl Strands are individually hand-strung to order. However, a small selection is available for timely gifting and immediate shipping.
